### 1. List Explore Feed - Geospatial Distance Search (Radius of 100km from Lat/Lng coordinates)
GET {{baseUrl}}/explore/list?latitude=37.774929&longitude=-122.419416&radius=100
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 2. List Explore Feed - Viewport Bounding Box Map Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/explore/list?limit=1000&north=40.800000&south=40.700000&east=-73.900000&west=-74.000000
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 3. List Explore Feed - Latest/Newest sorting (no location)
GET {{baseUrl}}/explore/list?filter=latest
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 4. List Explore Feed - Specific Category ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/explore/list?categoryId=65eb1a4b89f89b001234abcd
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 5. Get Share URL for an Event
GET {{baseUrl}}/explore/share-url?id=6a2904739f3feca6e22f4f98&type=event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 6. Get Share URL for a Course
GET {{baseUrl}}/explore/share-url?id=6a2904769f3feca6e22f5928&type=course
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 7. Search events & courses (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/explore/search?q=tenniss
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 11. Save a search query to history (Authenticated)
POST {{baseUrl}}/explore/recent-searches
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "tenniss"
}


### 8. Fetch recent 6 searches (Authenticated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/explore/recent-searches
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 9. Delete a specific recent search query
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/explore/recent-searches?query=test
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 10. Clear all recent searches
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/explore/recent-searches
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 12. Fetch trending searches (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/explore/trending-searches
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 13. Search filtering by type events (returns active events sorted by startDate ascending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/explore/search?type=events
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 14. Search filtering by type courses (returns active courses sorted by startDate ascending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/explore/search?type=courses
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 15. Search filtering by categoryId
GET {{baseUrl}}/explore/search?categoryId=65eb1a4b89f89b001234abcd
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### 16. Search filtering by categoryId AND search term
GET {{baseUrl}}/explore/search?q=test&categoryId=65eb1a4b89f89b001234abcd
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}



